        "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557682250-33bd709cbe85?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1400",
        "prompt": "A glowing network of interconnected nodes and data streams on a dark background, representing a proprietary algorithm framework.",
        "alt": "自主算法框架示意图"
      }
    },
    {
      "heading": "平台适配瓶颈",
      "body": "与国产XR平台（如PICO）及工业仿真软件（如Unity中国版）的接口适配方案不足，难以满足数据安全与生态融合需求。项目明确创新目标，聚焦国产平台无缝对接，为高校虚拟实训、工业数字孪生等场景提供安全、兼容的解决方案。",
      "image": {
        "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496171367470-9ed9a91ea931?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1400",
        "prompt": "A person wearing a VR headset and data gloves, interacting with a holographic industrial simulation interface showing Chinese software logos.",
        "alt": "与国产平台适配的虚拟交互场景"
      }
    },
    {
      "heading": "产业痛点交叉分析",
      "body": "通过实地调研北方机器人等3家代表性企业，结论与产业“交互依赖传统手柄、自然交互能力薄弱”的核心痛点高度契合。基于实证分析，项目定位为研发“龙影手套”高精度多模态交互解决方案，旨在突破自然交互硬件瓶颈，为元宇宙产业注入自主技术动能。",
      "image": {
        "url": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1400",
        "prompt": "A team of engineers and researchers in a meeting room, analyzing data on a large screen with charts and robot schematics, deep in discussion.",
        "alt": "团队进行产业痛点交叉分析会议"
      }
    }
  ]
}

